                    Job Responsibilities:



Make outbound calls to potential customers to promote and sell company services;



Conduct market research and analyze customer needs to provide personalized recommendations;



Manage customer relationships, answer inquiries, and improve customer satisfaction;



Meet daily/monthly sales targets.





Requirements:



Previous experience in telemarketing is preferred; remote work experience is a plus;



Fluent in English, with excellent communication and verbal skills;



Self-motivated and able to work independently in a remote environment;



Strong time management skills and the ability to meet deadlines;



Positive attitude, proactive work ethic, and a team-oriented mindset;



Basic computer skills;



Working hours: From 4:00 AM to 12:00 PM, with a 1-hour break in between; Monday to Friday.



Work environment must be quiet and free of any animal noises, especially roosters crowing or dogs barking.





We Offer:



Flexible working hours with the ability to work from home, saving commute time;



Competitive salary and commission structure;



Comprehensive training and ongoing career development opportunities;



A supportive team environment and a great work culture;



Long-term employment opportunities with potential for advancement.





How to Apply:



Please send your resume and a brief self-introduction recording link. We will contact suitable candidates promptly.
